HR NO. 99 ENROLLED
WHEREAS, the tenth anniversary of The Melissa & David Show on April 1, 2026,
marks a significant milestone, and Melissa Frost and David Atwood are most deserving of
the highest recognition for their outstanding contributions to Central Louisiana.
THEREFORE, BE IT RESOLVED that the House of Representatives of the
Legislature of Louisiana does hereby commend and congratulate Melissa Frost and David
Atwood on the celebration of the tenth anniversary of The Melissa & David Show and does
hereby extend best wishes for continued success in the years to come.
